PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION whereby the BUFFALO POINT FIRST NATION BAND (a) surrenders, until May 7, 2089, any of its rights and interest in certain portions of Buffalo Point Indian Reserve No. 36 in MANITOBA, for the purpose of leasing them, and (b) extends the duration of a designation made in 1991.
